cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS 

The paper deals with heuristics for solving the maximin problem in the generative adversarial privacy setting for linear and convolutional neural network adversaries. This involves techniques from machine learning, privacy, and optimization, which are all covered by the above sub-categories. Specifically, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category as the paper deals with heuristics for solving a machine learning problem. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper deals with privacy in the adversarial setting. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper deals with neural networks and their optimization. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper deals with convolutional neural networks. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper deals with heuristics and optimization algorithms.
